703376f-b.title: Brooklyn: Bush Street - Columbia Street
703376f-b.text:
Bush Street (trees thereon), south side, east from Columbia
to Clinton Streets. In the backmround on Clinton and Bush Streets
is the Sapolin Co. building. Also shown is 501-507 Columbia Street,
south from Bush Street. Most of the seen area in this view will
be demolished and the buildings replaced with low cost apartments.
June 9, 1938.
P. L. Sperr
